Package: trdizinR
Title: Search TRDizin
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Emrah", "Er", , "eer@eremrah.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The trdizinR package provides a streamlined interface for accessing the TR Dizin (Türkiye Atıf Dizini) API, enabling researchers to search and retrieve metadata about scholarly publications, journals, authors, and institutions indexed in the TR Dizin database. It includes high-level functions for querying data (search_publication(), search_journal(), search_author(), search_institution()), as well as functions to fetch detailed records using unique identifiers (get_publication_detail(), get_journal_detail(), get_author_detail(), get_institution_detail()). The package supports flexible faceted search queries and returns parsed JSON responses as R lists, facilitating seamless integration into bibliometric analyses, academic dashboards, or research automation pipelines.
